author: Esther Castillejo, Enjoli Francis
title: Fauci to David Muir: US return to normal will not be like a 'light switch' turned on
description: He discussed with the ABC News anchor what would be needed for the U.S. to get back to normal, a possible second return of COVID-19 and testing.
content:
Dr. Anthony Fauci told ABC News anchor David Muir that when it comes to the U.S. returning to normal after the COVID-19 crisis, "it's going to be different in different parts of the country, depending on a number of factors."
